    • Constructor Detail

      • Search

        public Search()
        Populates the hashmap with the animal objects that contain the data for each animal in the shelter, then initializes the application. At this window, the user can search for an animal by case number or create a new entry. If the user searches for a case number that is not in the inventory, the screen will advance to the General Inventory Form where the user can then enter the information for a new entry to be assigned to that case number.
